data.description: *Seller willing to contribute towards closing costs or rate buy down* Nestled on 2.5 acres of serene countryside, this farmhouse offers sweeping mountain views. A perfect blend of rustic charm and modern comforts, the home features a welcoming formal dining room, a farmhouse kitchen bathed in natural light, a cozy living room, and a dedicated media room complete with a projector and screen. Outside, the gently terraced property showcases fruit trees, a 3-car garage, and a dog run. Located in a quiet, friendly neighborhood, this farmhouse presents an exciting opportunity for those looking to add their personal touch and create their dream home amidst the tranquility and natural beauty of the mountainside.
